(7, 'PELAJARAN 7', 'Chotto matte kudasai<br/> <br/>Tunggulah Sebentar', 'media/upload//2018/02/pelajaran7.jpg', '<p style="text-align:center"><img alt="" width="860" height="507" src="http://localhost/japunis.com//media/upload//2018/02/lesson7.jpg" /></p><div style="text-align:center" class="ckeditor-html5-audio"><audio controls="controls" src="http://localhost/japunis.com//media/upload//2018/02/lesson7_d1.mp3" controlslist="nodownload">&nbsp;</audio></div><hr /><p><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">Suzuki dan Schmidt berada di sebuah titik pertemuan untuk menghadiri pertandingan sepak bola. Mereka sedang menunggu Sato dan Ryan.</span></p><table style="width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="height:21px; text-align:right; width:15%"><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt"><strong>&nbsp;Sc:</strong></span></td><td style="height:21px; width:85%"><span style="color:#ff6600; font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">Ohayoo gozaimasu.</span></td></tr><tr><td style="height:17px; text-align:right; width:15%"><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">&nbsp;<strong>Su:</strong></span></td><td style="height:17px; width:85%"><span style="color:#ff6600; font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">Ohayoo gozaimasu.</span></td></tr><tr><td style="height:17px; text-align:right; width:15%"><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt"><strong>Sc:</strong></span></td><td style="height:17px; width:85%"><span style="color:#ff6600; font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">Sakkaa no shiai wa gogo ichi-ji kara desu ne.</span></td></tr><tr><td style="height:17px; text-align:right; width:15%"><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt"><strong>&nbsp;Su:</strong></span></td><td style="height:17px; width:85%"><span style="color:#ff6600; font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">Ee.</span></td></tr><tr><td style="height:17px; text-align:right; width:15%"><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt"><strong>Sc:</strong></span></td><td style="height:17px; width:85%"><span style="color:#ff6600; font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">Sato-san to, Ryan-san wa?</span></td></tr><tr><td style="height:17px; text-align:right; width:15%"><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">&nbsp;<strong>Su:</strong></span></td><td style="height:17px; width:85%"><span style="color:#ff6600; font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">Sugu koko e kimasu kara, chotto matte kudasai.</span></td></tr><tr><td style="height:17px; text-align:right; width:15%"><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt"><strong>Sc:</strong></span></td><td style="height:17px; width:85%"><span style="color:#ff6600; font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">Hai, wakarimashita.</span></td></tr></tbody></table><hr /><table style="width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="height:17px; text-align:right; width:15%"><span style="font-size:12pt"><strong><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif">Sc:</span></strong></span></td><td style="height:17px; width:85%"><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">Selamat pagi.</span></td></tr><tr><td style="height:17px; text-align:right; width:15%"><span style="font-size:12pt"><strong><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif">&nbsp;Su:</span></strong></span></td><td style="height:17px; width:85%"><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">Selamat pagi.</span></td></tr><tr><td style="height:17px; text-align:right; width:15%"><span style="font-size:12pt"><strong><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif">&nbsp;Sc:</span></strong></span></td><td style="height:17px; width:85%"><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">Pertandingan sepak bola dimulai dari jam 1 siang, kan?</span></td></tr><tr><td style="height:17px; text-align:right; width:15%"><span style="font-size:12pt"><strong><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif">Su:</span></strong></span></td><td style="height:17px; width:85%"><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">Ya.</span></td></tr><tr><td style="height:17px; text-align:right; width:15%"><span style="font-size:12pt"><strong><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif">&nbsp;Sc:</span></strong></span></td><td style="height:17px; width:85%"><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">Bagaimana dengan Sato dan Ryan?</span></td></tr><tr><td style="height:17px; text-align:right; width:15%"><span style="font-size:12pt"><strong><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif">&nbsp;S:</span></strong></span></td><td style="height:17px; width:85%"><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">Mereka akan segera datang ke sini, jadi tunggu sebentar.</span></td></tr><tr><td style="height:17px; text-align:right; width:15%"><span style="font-size:12pt"><strong><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif">Sc:</span></strong></span></td><td style="height:17px; width:85%"><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">Ya, baiklah.</span></td></tr></tbody></table><hr /><p><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:14pt">Kosa Kata</span></p><table style="width:100%"><tbody><tr><td><strong><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">chotto matte kudasai</span></strong></td><td><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">tunggu sebentar</span></td></tr><tr><td><strong><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">chotto</span></strong></td><td><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">sesaat</span></td></tr><tr><td><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:16px"><strong>machimasu</strong></span></span></td><td><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">sebentar</span></td></tr><tr><td><strong><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">ohayoo gozaimasu</span></strong></td><td><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">selamat pagi</span></td></tr><tr><td><strong><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">sugu</span></strong></td><td><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">segera</span></td></tr><tr><td><strong><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">kimasu</span></strong></td><td><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">datang</span></td></tr></tbody></table>', '<div style="text-align:center" class="ckeditor-html5-audio"><audio controls="controls" src="http://localhost/japunis.com//media/upload//2018/02/lesson7_d2.mp3" controlslist="nodownload">&nbsp;</audio></div><hr /><p><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">Percakapan di stadion.</span></p><table style="width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="height:21px; text-align:right; width:15%"><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt"><strong>&nbsp;Sc:</strong></span></td><td style="height:21px; width:85%"><span style="color:#ff6600; font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">Kawasaki Frontale wa donna chiimu desu ka.</span></td></tr><tr><td style="height:17px; text-align:right; width:15%"><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">&nbsp;<strong>Sa:</strong></span></td><td style="height:17px; width:85%"><span style="color:#ff6600; font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">Totemo tsuyoi chiimu desu yo.</span></td></tr><tr><td style="height:17px; text-align:right; width:15%"><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt"><strong>R:</strong></span></td><td style="height:17px; width:85%"><span style="color:#ff6600; font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">Fujitsu wa Kawasaki Frontale no suponsaa desu.</span></td></tr><tr><td style="height:17px; text-align:right; width:15%"><span style="font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></td><td style="height:17px; width:85%"><span style="color:#ff6600; font-family:roboto,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">Watashitachi minna de